    "description": "When a hero guild saves the village of Torden from a kobold threat, tavern keeper Herb is inspired to pursue his own heroic journey.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082310/extras/046fd9f65976931b05e31851bba8ee9f.webp?t=1728599756\" width=616 height=36 /></span><br><br>PixelQuest - Herb's Adventure offers a nostalgic experience in the vein of classic 16-bit RPGs. Immerse yourself in a richly crafted world, interact with a wide range of NPCs, engage in tactical battles, and discover powerful new equipment. Whether you follow the main storyline or explore side quests, you'll encounter a host of intriguing characters and stories.<br><br>Level up, enhance your attributes, and customize your combat dice with new faces. Develop your skills and spells through an extensive skill tree spanning four key attributes: Strength, Agility, Skill, and Talent. Choose your path to become a melee powerhouse or a versatile battle mage.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082310/extras/bcefadc59de0434635a89d3814c89da6.webp?t=1728599756\" width=616 height=36 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082310/extras/c972355aaba88832864b92df1c7c2520.poster.avif?t=1728599756\" width=618 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082310/extras/c972355aaba88832864b92df1c7c2520.webm?t=1728599756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082310/extras/c972355aaba88832864b92df1c7c2520.mp4?t=1728599756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Tactical Dice Combat System:</strong> Engage in strategic battles using combat dice. Equip a variety of weapons, armor, and shields to gain additional dice, and use experience points to unlock and improve die faces.<br></li><li><strong>Deep Skill Tree:</strong> Tailor your character's growth with a comprehensive skill tree. Focus on Strength for powerful melee attacks, Agility for defense, Skill for special abilities, or Talent for potent spells.<br></li><li><strong>Many Abilities and Items:</strong> Use rerolls, techs, and spells to maximize your potential in every encounter. Utilize items like healing potions, throwing darts, and smoke bombs to turn the tide in tough battles.<br></li><li><strong>Engaging Exploration:</strong> Traverse a vibrant world filled with secrets and side quests. Meet unique characters, uncover hidden lore, and experience a story rich with humor and heart.</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082310/extras/6cc49231fb6f34b248524ca82727330b.webp?t=1728599756\" width=616 height=36 /></span><br><br>PixelQuest - Herb's Adventure is an officially licensed fan game set in the universe of the YouTube tabletop RPG campaign &quot;DEMID - Das erste Mal im Dungeon&quot; by B4Pixel. Your purchase supports B4Pixel and future TTRPG productions.<br><br>While it draws inspiration from the official campaign, Herb's Adventure is a standalone story that welcomes both fans and newcomers to the world of DEMID.",
